      "value": "<p>You touch a willing creature who you can see. You impart upon them eyes of absolute authority. Affected creature gains 60 Feet of Dark Vision that see's through all forms of Chakra based Darkness.</p><p>Additionally, creatures who gain Darkvision as a result of this jutsu gain truesight against Genjutsu of A-Rank or lower.</p><p>If this jutsu is cast again, while currently affecting another creature, it ends on that other creature immediately.</p>",
